abstract: >
  This repository supports MSc research at Ulster University exploring the integration of Sentinel-1/2 and UAV data for UKHab-aligned habitat classification and natural-capital monitoring. It includes workflows for data fusion, accuracy assessment, and change detection in support of rewilding and ecosystem accounting.
